snippet.title: Cities Skylines II | Announcement Trailer I
snippet.description:
Wishlisting is open now!

If you can dream it, you can build it. The highly acclaimed hit Cities: Skylines is now revolutionizing the city-builder genre again. The sequel to one of the best-selling management games of its decade is coming in 2023. Get ready for a new epic scale in the most realistic city builder - ever.

https://www.paradoxinteractive.com/games/cities-skylines-ii

Wishlist directly on the Store Pages;
https://www.microsoft.com/store/p/cities-skylines-ii/9NH213LRNGPC
https://store.playstation.com/concept/232640
https://store.steampowered.com/app/949230/Cities_Skylines_II
